org.barghos.core.api.tuple

Interface ITup3fW

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITupfW
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IColor3W, IHDRColor3W, ILDRColor3W
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HDRColor3, LDRColor3, Tup3f

    public interface ITup3fW
extends ITupfW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 3-dimensional float tuple.
